  - Data Visualization: minimal charts with subdued grids; use accent colors for important signals.
  - Interactive elements: accessible, keyboard-navigable, focus-visible styling with the specified focus color.
  - Micro-interactions: transitions of 150–220ms for hovers, 300ms for panel expansions.

- Visual Style

