- Runtime Safety (Mandatory Coding Standards):
  - Supabase query results: use const items = data ?? [].
  - Array methods guarded: (items ?? []).map(...) or Array.isArray(items) ? items.map(...) : [].
  - React useState for arrays/objects: useState<Type[]>([]) defaults.
  - API response validation: const list = Array.isArray(response?.data) ? response.data : [].
  - Optional chaining: obj?.property?.nested
  - Destructuring with defaults: const { items = [], count = 0 } = response ?? {}.

